title: Episode 298: Rollie Polly Porn Connoisseur (Feat. Miguel)
itunes:title: Episode 298: Rollie Polly Porn Connoisseur (Feat. Miguel)
description:
Singer/songwriter, Miguel joins the ladies of Lip Service this week to promote his upcoming project 'Art Dealer Chic Vol. 4." Miguel opens up about his cats intruding when he and his wife are trying to get intimate, the odd conversations he'll have with his friends about porn, and much more. Miguel even shares a story (pre-marriage) about the time he popped up on a not-so-trustworthy woman he was seeing at the time. Enjoy!
